<p><strong style="background-color: #eacf32;">Cash flow from Operations</strong></p>
<p>In fact, this is one of the most important checks one needs to run before deciding to invest in a company. The company should generate cash flows from operations; this is, in fact, where the proof of the pudding lies. A company which is draining cash from operations raises some sort of red flag.</p>
